                            <comment id="13009861" author="stack" created="Tue, 22 Mar 2011 21:52:27 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;Well, at mo. RS gets info from Master that it uses to finish startup; e.g. hbase.rootdir (we used get the &apos;address&apos; to use but thats just broke and will be fixed in hbase-1502).  In fact 1502 should help a bunch in here.&lt;/p&gt;</comment>
                            <comment id="13029159" author="stack" created="Thu, 5 May 2011 06:22:12 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;I think we should resolve this issue.  1502 went in.  We handle ServerNotRunningException now (hbase-3687).&lt;/p&gt;</comment>
